sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant FS as File System
    participant Hub as Orchestrator Hub
    participant Test as Test Spoke
    participant SLM as SLM Pool
    participant Readme as Readme Spoke
    participant Git as Git
    
    Note over Dev,Git: Development Workflow
    
    Dev->>FS: Writes/Modifies Code
    FS-->>Hub: File Change Event
    
    Hub->>Test: Trigger Test Generation
    Test->>FS: Read Changed Files
    Test->>SLM: Analyze Code (codellama:7b)
    SLM-->>Test: Code Structure
    
    Test->>SLM: Generate Tests (DeepSeek 7B)
    SLM-->>Test: Test Code
    
    Test->>FS: Write Test Files
    Test->>Test: Run Tests
    
    alt Tests Pass
        Test-->>Hub: Tests Passed
        Hub->>Readme: Trigger Doc Update
        
        Readme->>FS: Read Code + Tests
        Readme->>SLM: Extract Examples (codellama:7b)
        SLM-->>Readme: Examples
        
        Readme->>SLM: Summarize API (Gemma 2B)
        SLM-->>Readme: API Docs
        
        Readme->>FS: Update README.md
        Readme->>Git: Commit Changes
        Git-->>Dev: Updated Docs
        
    else Tests Fail
        Test->>SLM: Analyze Failure (DeepSeek 7B)
        SLM-->>Test: Failure Explanation
        
        Test-->>Hub: Report Failures
        Hub-->>Dev: Test Report + Explanations
        
        Note over Dev: Developer Fixes Code
        Dev->>FS: Fix Code
        FS-->>Hub: New Change Event
        Note over Hub,Git: Cycle Repeats
    end
    
    Note over Hub,SLM: Squeeze Mechanism Active
    Hub->>Hub: Monitor CPU/Memory
    alt High Load
        Hub->>Test: Reduce Concurrency
        Hub->>Readme: Throttle Generation
    end
    
    Note over FS,Git: Audit Trail
    Test->>Hub: Log Test Generation
    Readme->>Hub: Log Doc Update
    Hub->>Hub: Write Audit Log